# Build artifacts — never copy host builds into the image
**/bin/
**/obj/

# Local dev / IDE
**/*.user
.vs/
*.suo

# Secrets & local config (image is configured via compose env vars)
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/appsettings.*.local.json

# Docker / compose files (not needed inside the image)
Dockerfile
.dockerignore
docker-compose.yml

# Misc
**/*.md
sms-gateway/config.yml
sms-gateway/fcm-credentials.json
